Node.Notes: Tree assumes: [Does he cause] ones being weaned from milk [and] those taken from the breasts [to understand?]
Precise meaning unclear. Suggestions have ranged from speaking in tongues to being code-words for great thoughts. Perhaps drunken teacher repeating letters of the alphabet.
Apparently drunken teacher teaching the alphabet turned into instrument of judgment. Tsaw understood as derived from command; qaw from line, little ones becomes impersonal a little.
Uncertain. Tree assumes something like: [If] one drives the wheel of his cart [over it], he does not crush it with his horses. See WBC commentary.
